Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(All of us) us, us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.60,0:00:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Dream save us us) us, all of us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The end of a dream, the end of the sea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We all have different places we want to go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But first, we need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To make a shining legend out of ourselves{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Sparks fly, no limit\NThis is where it starts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.75,0:00:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,ONE PIECE{\i1}!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.38,0:00:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All of us, I ask you travelers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are your dreams still pure?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sleepless cells are shaken and burst{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:01:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, all of us\NIn the middle of an adventure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}All of us, I tell you travelers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.02,0:01:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}No such thing as a pointless fight{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When random contexts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.12,0:01:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Start to make sense on their own{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The threads of time are spun back together{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}The world keeps changing along with us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(All of us) us, us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}(Dream save us us) us, all of us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.60,0:01:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The World Is Shaken! The Ruler's Judgment\Nand the Five Elders' Actions!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While the murder of King Cobra\Nwas kept hidden,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.91,0:01:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the curtain came down on the Reverie.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He must still be around! Let's catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.77,0:02:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,King Cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.37,0:02:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.37,0:02:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot collapse here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.59,0:02:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I must tell Luffy and Princess Vivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,King Cobra's words!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you found them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra-sama hasn't returned\Nfrom his meeting with the Five Elders...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.11,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And we have no idea where Vivi-sama went.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.94,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on in Mary Geoise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about\NCobra-sama's condition, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll search the castle one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'll look for Vivi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pell, search from the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see King Cobra!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We were told not to allow anyone in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Our king is sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.74,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cobra-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Has anyone seen Princess Vivi of\Nthe Kingdom of Alabasta?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Princess Vivi! Have you seen her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:04:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Vivi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,King Seki, Princess Comane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to escort you to the ship\Nat the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hide!\N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez! It's just a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.57,0:06:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask you to come with me,\Nso don't tell me what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,These ones next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.88,0:06:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.46,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a royal family's baggage.\NTreat it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.76,0:06:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Wapol!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hide in those boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good idea, isn't it? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll find us! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for escorting them.\NThe marines will take over from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.04,0:06:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,King Tea IV is on board now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up with bringing in the luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.27,0:07:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.74,0:07:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We managed to sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.03,0:07:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But what should I do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.29,0:07:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to tell the world\Nwhat happened at the Reverie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.92,0:07:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do that,\Nthe Government will kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Or should I turn you over\Nto marine soldiers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But just like me,\Nyou don't want to be found, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.85,0:07:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.18,0:07:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since I witnessed the dark side of\Nthe Government...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.23,0:08:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.61,0:08:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do these things keep happening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! I'm sure he won't let me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.12,0:08:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I have the type of story\Nthat he craves...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A Transponder Snail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.91,0:08:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you had it! Can I borrow it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.29,0:08:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cheapskate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my lifeline!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.80,0:08:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.93,0:08:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mor-chan! It's me, Wapol!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.52,0:08:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How was the Reverie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's not important!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.11,0:08:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet something happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't talk about it over the Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll kill me if they find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I want you to harbor me\Nin exchange for my story!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What country's ship is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Eigis Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay. We'll approach the ship\Npretending to be researching a story.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Use that chance to get aboard ours.\NDon't let anyone see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.26,0:09:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.97,0:09:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,News so big\Nthat a king's life is threatened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.40,0:09:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So what exactly did you see, Wapol?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the last person\NI want to tell about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go back to your people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It was CP-0 who captured me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.17,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I meet up with my people,\Nthey'll take me again by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So let me use your Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to call my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.01,0:09:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.26,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the last thing you should do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.72,0:10:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Let me just use it for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.24,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHIP OF THE TAJINE KINGDOM\N(SHIP'S HOLD)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}I'm hungry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.70,0:10:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,SHIP OF THE KINGDOM OF LULUSIA\N(SHIP BOTTOM)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I get to Lulusia,\Neverything'll be alright...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, Sabo-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.72,0:10:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Live on!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.47,0:10:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Vivi, Wapol...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a few other stowaways\Nlurked on the ships...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.77,0:10:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that were taking various monarchs\Nback to their homes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It didn't take long before the murder\Nof Cobra, King of the Kingdom of Alabasta,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:11:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the disappearance of Princess Vivi\Nbecame known worldwide.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,HOLY LAND MARY GEOISE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sabo is another man with a strange fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No one is surrounded by "D"\Nmore than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to put an end\Nto that Egghead matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ring, ring, ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.14,0:11:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Clank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Imu-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.56,0:11:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to use the Mother Flame\Nthat Vegapunk invented.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.98,0:11:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, if we don't try it, we'll never know\Nif that thing is real or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's figure out what to do with Egghead\Nbased on the results of that experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The testing site should be in areas\Nwith forests rather than at sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kingdom of Lulusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a lot of people live there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.05,0:11:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It doesn't matter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The world should be\Nas the Creators want it to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you choose Lulusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.36,0:12:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make the necessary preparations.\NWe request your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In Lulusia, there are signs of revolt\Namong the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This will serve as a good lesson\Nfor everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually,\Nwhen we have that power at our disposal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The long battle will come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.32,0:12:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Vivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:12:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ST. JAYGARCIA SATURN\NGODHEAD OF SCIENCE & DEFENSE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.99,0:13:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,ST. MARCUS MARS\NGODHEAD OF ENVIRONMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,ST. TOPMAN WARCURY\NGODHEAD OF JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ST. ETHANBARON V. NUSJURO\NGODHEAD OF FINANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.62,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ST. SHEPHERD JU PETER\NGODHEAD OF AGRICULTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,MARINE HEADQUARTERS, NEW WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A report for Fleet Admiral Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There are revolts in the Tajine Kingdom\Nand the Eigis Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.15,0:13:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Just crush every last one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.08,0:13:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up! Load ammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.38,0:13:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Deploy all the Seraphim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! We'll launch the Seraphim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Marines were extremely busy with\Nthe abolition of the Seven Warlords system{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the uprisings\Nin various affiliated countries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, this was also\Nthe start of the new Marines.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.10,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.81,0:14:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe\Nthere's been one revolt after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodile showed up\Non the Emptee Bluffs Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.82,0:14:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sables!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,KAMABAKKA QUEENDOM\NPEACHY ISLAND, GRAND LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as\Nwe arrived at the Kingdom of Lulusia,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.42,0:14:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,King Seki and Princess Comane\Ngot captured...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,by the people who were waiting for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and just get me out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a stowaway, but they welcomed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's because\Nyou were their best hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when I saw the newspaper article\Nfor the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and learned that I was framed\Nfor the King's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Unsurprisingly,\Npeople considered me a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to tell the truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but I held my tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I felt their growing thirst\Nfor revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to the influence of Betty and others,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.85,0:15:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,there were many people in Lulusia\Nwho wanted to join the Revolutionary Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.10,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're the ones I brought here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.15,0:15:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do,\Nyou pieces of trash?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.40,0:15:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get killed or fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose your own destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Betty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, I couldn't get an Encryption\NTransponder Snail in Lulusia,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.04,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wasn't able to call you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.25,0:16:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But I made an indirect call as soon as\Nwe sailed out, and that was the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.76,0:16:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dragon-san!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,King Cobra's assassin...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.69,0:16:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure the Government\Neavesdropped on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and thought I was in Lulusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.07,0:16:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But in reality, I was already out at sea\Nwith the enlistees.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.12,0:16:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You were on the call\Nwhen it happened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The destruction of the Kingdom of Lulusia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.58,0:16:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.79,0:16:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There was panic on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So many people left their families behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,They saw their home island\Nblown away in front of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.72,0:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What exactly happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.18,0:17:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A large shadow covered the sky above...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the next moment, it was already...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A large shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be anything biological\Nor natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Something really dark\Nwas flying over the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Sabo,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you mentioned Imu earlier, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.39,0:17:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This may sound rather bizarre to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but among the First Twenty\Nwho created this world 800 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.32,0:17:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a king named Saint Imu\Nfrom the Nerona Dynasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.32,0:17:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We know there is an ability\Nto make someone immortal in this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But this means that\Nsomeone has actually used it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's proof that there's a person out there\Nwho doesn't know death!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying that's the person I saw?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's just a coincidence\Nthat they have the same name...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But who else would the Five Elders\Nhumble themselves to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.51,0:18:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the highest authority\Namong the Celestial Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,who flatter themselves\Nto be descendants of gods!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,One more surprising thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.86,0:18:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If the thing that you saw\Ndestroying the country from the clouds
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,was a Government weapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,only Vegapunk\Ncould have made such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Iva.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.70,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Vegapunk wouldn't make such a blatant tool\Nfor killing people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.58,0:18:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So what if it was an Ancient Weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If Imu is an ancient, living person,\Nit makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin confirmed the existence of\Nthe Ancient Weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.31,0:19:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But if they had it,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't they use it until now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And why use it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Present day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Celestial Dragon has just been executed\Nin the Holy Land Mary Geoise today.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However,\Nit will never be reported to the world.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.38,0:19:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good riddance-{\i1}eh{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he sided with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,fools in the lower world\Nhave been pushing their luck recently-{\i1}eh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all his fault\Nthat we lost our food supply-{\i1}eh{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The judge was a man who was once active as\Na champion on an island called God Valley.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He is now the Supreme Commander of\Nthe Holy Knights.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.86,0:19:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}St. Figarland Garling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The one executed...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was the man who defended the Fish-Men.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}St. Donquixote Myosgard.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who defends scum\Nis lower than scum they protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How far I have run{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Without knowing it, I counted scars{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A treasure map in my head all along{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still looking for the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The real promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lies much deeper in my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:21:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A dream{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That no one can catch up with{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.56,0:21:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's all I hold on to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To you who smiles like the sun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll sing the same song as that day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This wish I don't want to forget\NEven when I grow up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until it reaches you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dive into the Sea of Information!\NThe Punk Records Library!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Lilith, one of the Satellites of\NDr. Vegapunk, the genius scientist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Edison, also Vegapunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Today we'll introduce this one!\NNefertari Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She is the princess of\Nthe Kingdom of Alabasta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and Nefertari Cobra's only daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.37,0:22:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}She was born on February 2nd
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and likes curry, custard pudding,\Nand {\i1}mulukhiyah{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.67,0:22:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When she learned of\Nthe existence of Baroque Works,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which threatened the Kingdom of Alabasta,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.51,0:22:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,she infiltrated the organization herself\Nto find out who the mastermind was.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.05,0:22:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She used the alias Ms. Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,After she started working with\Nthe Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,she returned to the Kingdom of Alabasta,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.56,0:22:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and together with them, she foiled\NCrocodile's plot to overthrow the kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we ever meet again some day...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,will you call me your friend again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.08,0:22:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Vivi stayed in her beloved homeland, but\Nher ties to the Straw Hats remain deep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.96,0:22:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, she was kidnapped by CP-0\Nin the Holy Land Mary Geoise,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.75,0:23:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but she managed to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.05,0:23:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a little worried that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.30,0:23:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,she'll still be targeted\Nby a lot of people in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.30,0:23:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've seen it,\Ndonate to our research fund!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.89,0:23:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See you next time!
